msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/date"
msgid "December 29th, 1941 · Feodosia, Crimea, Ukraine"
msgstr "29 de diciembre de 1941 - Feodosia, Crimea, Ucrania"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/gameover/failed"
msgid ""
"The squad led by Lieutenant Arkady F. Aydinov could not establish control "
"over the bridgehead."
msgstr ""
"La escuadra dirigida por el teniente Arkady F. Aydinov no pudo establecer el "
"control sobre la cabeza de puente."

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/hints/pistol_holder"
msgid ""
"To signal other troops, fire a flare at the pier. The squad leader has the "
"flare gun in his inventory."
msgstr ""
"Para hacer señales a otras tropas, dispara una bengala al embarcadero. El "
"jefe de escuadra tiene la pistola de bengalas en su inventario."

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/name"
msgid "Red Tide"
msgstr "Marea Roja"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/name_big"
msgid "Red Tide"
msgstr "Marea Roja"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/narrator/aydinov/armor"
msgid ""
"The Fascists brought in their vehicles! Use the full firepower of the "
"gunboat and destroy them."
msgstr ""
"¡Los fascistas han traído sus vehículos! Utiliza toda la potencia de fuego "
"de la embarcación y destrúyelos."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/narrator/aydinov/boat_crash_01"
msgid ""
"Scum! The nervedragging anti-tank guns here! Comrades, we must silence those "
"guns immediately."
msgstr ""
"¡Escoria! ¡Aquí están los malditos cañones antitanque! Camaradas, debemos "
"encargarnos de esos cañones inmediatamente."

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/narrator/aydinov/clear_01"
msgid ""
"Well done, marines. A strong showing. Looks like the Germans didn't expect "
"us. But we should not relax too early - they will surely try to retake this "
"ground."
msgstr ""
"Bien hecho, marines. Una demostración de fuerza. Parece que los alemanes no "
"nos esperaban. Pero no debemos relajarnos demasiado: seguro que intentarán "
"retomar este pedazo de tierra."

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/narrator/aydinov/defense_01"
msgid ""
"Here they come, the bastards. Didn't take them long. We must hold this line "
"- the outcome of the operation depends on this very patch of land. Get to "
"work, comrades."
msgstr ""
"Ahí vienen, los muy cabrones. No han tardado mucho. Debemos mantener la "
"línea: el resultado de la operación depende precisamente de este pedazo de "
"tierra. A trabajar, camaradas."

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/narrator/aydinov/flare_01"
msgid ""
"Good work, boys - the lighthouse is secured. Now fire the flare and let the "
"others know. They're likely already worried sick over there."
msgstr ""
"Buen trabajo, chicos: el faro está asegurado. Ahora dispara la bengala y "
"avisa a los demás. Es probable que estén muy preocupados."

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/narrator/aydinov/flare_02"
msgid "The entrance is free!"
msgstr "¡La entrada es gratuita!"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/narrator/aydinov/landing_01"
msgid ""
"Let's go, comrades! We need to take that lighthouse and signal a flare - "
"without it, no reinforcements will come. We won't last long standing in the "
"open like this!"
msgstr ""
"¡Vamos, camaradas! Tenemos que tomar ese faro y señalar una bengala: sin "
"ella, no vendrán refuerzos. ¡No duraremos mucho tiempo en campo abierto!"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/narrator/aydinov/landing_02"
msgid ""
"Germans are bringing more from the south! Best to leave a few men behind to "
"cover the landing zone. We should not leave our rear uncovered."
msgstr ""
"¡Los alemanes traen más desde el sur! Es mejor dejar algunos hombres atrás "
"para cubrir la zona de desembarco. No debemos dejar nuestra retaguardia al "
"descubierto."

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/narrator/aydinov/mo4_control"
msgid ""
"The Germans are well dug in at the port. Our comrades will assault them, and "
"they will need naval support. I placed one of our gunboats under your "
"command. It's on the far side of the pier."
msgstr ""
"Los alemanes están bien atrincherados en el puerto. Nuestros camaradas les "
"asaltarán y necesitarán apoyo desde el mar. He puesto una de nuestras "
"embarcaciones bajo tu mando. Está al otro lado del muelle."

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/narrator/aydinov/mortars"
msgid ""
"Get down! Enemy mortar fire incoming! Expect the Germans to charge as soon "
"as the mortars stop firing!"
msgstr ""
"¡Al suelo! ¡Se aproxima fuego de mortero enemigo! ¡Seguro que los alemanes "
"atacan en cuanto los morteros dejen de disparar!"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/narrator/aydinov/plane_01"
msgid ""
"Enemy aircraft! It's going straight for the gunboat - shoot it down "
"immediately!"
msgstr ""
"¡Avión enemigo! Va directo hacia la la embarcación - ¡Derríbalo "
"inmediatamente!"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/narrator/aydinov/plane_02"
msgid ""
"Heads up - aircraft incoming from the west! It's preparing to strike the "
"gunboat!"
msgstr ""
"Atención: ¡viene un avión del oeste! ¡Se prepara para atacar nuestra "
"embarcación!"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/narrator/aydinov/plane_03"
msgid "Another plane approaches!"
msgstr "¡Se acerca otro avión!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/narrator/aydinov/port_cleared"
msgid ""
"Well done, comrades - the port is under our control now. Reinforcements "
"should arrive at any moment."
msgstr ""
"Bien hecho, camaradas: el puerto ya está bajo nuestro control. Los refuerzos "
"llegarán en cualquier momento."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/narrator/aydinov/preparation_01"
msgid ""
"Reinforcements have arrived - just in time. Let's use this short pause to "
"prepare for the enemy's counterattack."
msgstr ""
"Han llegado refuerzos, justo a tiempo. Aprovechemos esta breve pausa para "
"prepararnos para el contraataque del enemigo."

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/narrator/aydinov/retreat"
msgid ""
"They're falling back! We've done it, comrades! We held the line - and showed "
"the full strength of our Black Sea Fleet! Now our brothers in arms and "
"families in Sevastopol have a real chance to stand strong!"
msgstr ""
"¡Están retrocediendo! ¡Lo hemos conseguido, camaradas! ¡Mantuvimos la línea "
"y mostramos toda la fuerza de nuestra Flota del Mar Negro! ¡Ahora nuestros "
"camaradas y familias de Sebastopol tienen una oportunidad de aguantar!"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"Excellent work! The people and the garrison at Sevastopol will be thankful "
"for your victory"
msgstr ""
"¡Excelente trabajo! El pueblo y la guarnición de Sebastopol os agradecerán "
"vuestra victoria"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"Ouch! That is not the outcome Stavka planned. You don’t want this reported "
"to HQ. Maybe you should try again?"
msgstr ""
"¡Ay! Ese no es el resultado que Stavka había planeado. No querrás que se "
"informe de esto al Cuartel General. ¿Quizá deberías intentarlo de nuevo?"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/place"
msgid "Lt. Aydinov's landing party, Soviet Black Sea Fleet"
msgstr "Grupo de desembarco del teniente Aydinov, Flota soviética del Mar Negro"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/skip_preparation"
msgid "Skip preparation"
msgstr "Saltar preparación"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/story"
msgid ""
"You are going on a mission to support besieged Sevastopol. To be precise, "
"you are ordered to secure the Crimean harbor of Feodosiya for the large "
"invasion force that will land there. We will go ashore behind the enemy’s "
"back, and you will be in the first echelon"
msgstr ""
"Vas en misión de apoyo a la sitiada Sebastopol. Para ser precisos, se te "
"ordena asegurar el puerto crimeo de Feodosiya para la gran fuerza de "
"invasión que desembarcará allí. Desembarcaremos a espaldas del enemigo y tú "
"formarás parte de la primera oleada."

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/tasks/01-lighthouse"
msgid "Capture the lighthouse"
msgstr "Captura el faro"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/tasks/02-flare"
msgid "Fire a flare near the lighthouse"
msgstr "Dispara una bengala cerca del faro"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/tasks/03-clean"
msgid "Establish control over the port area"
msgstr "Establecer el control sobre la zona portuaria"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/tasks/04-pak36"
msgid "Capture or eliminate the AT guns"
msgstr "Captura o elimina los cañones AT"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/tasks/05-defense"
msgid "Hold the landing zone near the lighthouse"
msgstr "Mantén la zona de desembarco cerca del faro"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/tasks/06-mo4"
msgid "The gunboat under your command must survive"
msgstr "La embarcación bajo tu mando debe sobrevivir"

msgctxt "mission/single/06-bonus/1941_12_feodosia/timer"
msgid "German counter-attack:"
msgstr "Contraataque alemán:"
